    <h5><ng-container i18n="about.about-the-project">Specifications</ng-container><ng-templatengIf]="locale.substr(0, 2) === 'en'"> &trade;</ng-template></h5>
    <p i18n>Specifications

Essentially this is a full bitcoin fork, but:<br>
Block Reward = nFees*0.1 + GetBlockSubsidy()    // Burn rate is 90% of tx fees (https://www.blockchain.com/charts/transaction-fees)<br>
Block Weight <= 400,000;                                     // 10 times smaller than bitcoin<br>
100% Segwit                                                          // Eliminates problems with legacy types of transactions<br>
Halving Interval = 210000 blocks / 4;                    // Halving is every year (bitcoin halving is every 4 years)<br>
Block Subsidy = 50 * 4;                                         // 21 000 000 coins max<br>
Hashing algorithm for blocks is Keccak (sha-3).</p>
